- content_for(:title, "Reset Your Password — #{APP_NAME}")

%p Hi #{@user.display_name},

%p Someone requested a password reset for your #{APP_NAME} account. Click the link below to choose a new password:

%p= link_to "Reset Password", @reset_url

%p This link will expire in 2 hours.

%p If you did not request this change, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.

%p
  — #{APP_NAME}
